nodes.text: Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part I

Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part I was one of the canceled Bungo n' Rusti comics by James Anderson. In the story, Bungo Bung and Rusti were to have been forced into joining the Rebellion after Nien Nunb takes their cargo. It was continued in Bungo n' Rusti Join the Rebellion?!! Part II.
